<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Login pannello presenze EverGreen</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #06070b;
            --card: #121521;
            --line: rgba(170, 110, 255, 0.18);
            --text: #eef2ff;
            --muted: #a7b0c9;
            --purple: #8b4dff;
            --purple-2: #5f23cb;
            --green: #7eea57;
            --danger: #ff7e94;
            --shadow: 0 18px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.40);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 18px;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: var(--text);
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(139, 77, 255, 0.22), transparent 30%),
                radial-gradient(circle at right, rgba(126, 234, 87, 0.08), transparent 20%),
                linear-gradient(180deg, #05060a 0%, #090b12 100%);
        }

        .card {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 470px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(18, 21, 33, 0.98), rgba(13, 15, 23, 0.98));
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 26px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        .brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .brand img {
            width: 72px;
            height: 72px;
            object-fit: contain;
            border-radius: 18px;
            background: rgba(139, 77, 255, 0.14);
            padding: 8px;
        }

        .eyebrow {
            color: var(--green);
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.4px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        p {
            margin: 0 0 18px;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        input,
        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        input {
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            background: #0c0f18;
            color: white;
            border: 1px solid rgba(151, 116, 255, 0.18);
            outline: none;
        }

        input:focus {
            border-color: rgba(126, 234, 87, 0.65);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(126, 234, 87, 0.10);
        }

        button {
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: white;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple), var(--purple-2));
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(95, 35, 203, 0.35);
        }

        .error {
            background: rgba(255, 126, 148, 0.10);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 126, 148, 0.24);
            color: #ffd4dc;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="brand">
            <img src="/assets/evergreen-logo.png" alt="EverGreen logo" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
            <div>
                <div class="eyebrow">EverGreen Competitive Panel</div>
                <h1>Accesso admin</h1>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p>Inserisci il token admin del pannello web per gestire le presenze del roster competitivo.</p>

        <% if (error) { %>
            <div class="error">
                <%= error %>
            </div>
            <% } %>

                <form method="post" action="/login">
                    <input type="password" name="token" placeholder="Token admin" required />
                    <button type="submit">Accedi al pannello</button>
                </form>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
